PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773159076
OL,3,CHundreds of Wirral residents protest
OL,4,Cagainst Peak Cluster pipeline
OL,6,FHundreds of local residents have
OL,7,Fgathered in protest outside a town
OL,8,Fhall against a proposed 160-mile
OL,9,Fcarbon capture pipeline that would run
OL,10,Fthrough Cheshire and the Wirral.
OL,12,FThe #60 million project would
OL,13,Ftransport carbon captured in the Peak
OL,14,FDistrict through Cheshire and the
OL,15,FWirral before being deposited in
OL,16,Fdepleted Morecambe gas fields.
OL,18,FCouncillors debated the Peak Cluster
OL,19,Fproject at an extraordinary meeting at
OL,20,FWallasey Town Hall on Monday 9 March.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773159076
OL,3,CHundreds of Wirral residents protest
OL,4,Cagainst Peak Cluster pipeline
OL,6,FLocals have been critical of the
OL,7,Fproject over worries it could ruin the
OL,8,Fnatural landscapes and harm the
OL,9,Fwildlife.
OL,11,FBut the government says it is "vital"
OL,12,Ffor the country's future as it tries
OL,13,Fto meet its net zero targets.
OL,15,FLaura Beveridge, Chair of Action
OL,16,FAgainst CCS said: "We're opposed to it
OL,17,Fbecause there simply isn't enough
OL,18,Finformation. The consultation has been
OL,19,Freally poor."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773159076
OL,3,CHundreds of Wirral residents protest
OL,4,Cagainst Peak Cluster pipeline
OL,6,FShe added: "We've been dismissed,
OL,7,Fwe've been told 'we don't know, we're
OL,8,Funsure'. There is nothing set in stone.
OL,10,F"For an infrastructure project of this
OL,11,Fsize. we would expect as residents
OL,12,Fbeing directly affected by the
OL,13,Fpipeline that those questions should
OL,14,Fbe answered by now."
OL,16,FThe Government have rejected a
OL,17,Fpetition signed by 17,000 people to
OL,18,Fpause the project.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773159076
OL,3,CHundreds of Wirral residents protest
OL,4,Cagainst Peak Cluster pipeline
OL,6,FShe added: "We're not against the
OL,7,Fcement industries, we're not against
OL,8,Fnet zero.
OL,10,F"We appreciate that something needs to
OL,11,Fbe done. What we're asking is for them
OL,12,Fto find a better way.
OL,14,F"There are technologies out there that
OL,15,Fcan be used to capture carbon and
OL,16,Freuse it on site for energy."
OL,18,FAngie Davies, Labour Councillor for
OL,19,FLeasowe & Moreton East is also opposed
OL,20,Fto the project.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773159076
OL,3,CHundreds of Wirral residents protest
OL,4,Cagainst Peak Cluster pipeline
OL,6,F"We are going to carry on speaking up
OL,7,Ffor residents, saying our piece and
OL,8,Ffighting this all the way.
OL,10,F"The bottom line is we want this
OL,11,Fstopped. We want residents and our
OL,12,Fconcerns about safety heard.
OL,14,F"Environment is a factor we have got
OL,15,Flots of beautiful green space here on
OL,16,Fthe Wirral. Personally, the overriding
OL,17,Fconcern is safety and that's what
OL,18,Fpeople are telling me when I speak to
OL,19,Fthem."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
