FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773159076
OL,3,CHundreds of Wirral residents protest
OL,4,Cagainst Peak Cluster pipeline
OL,6,FThe Peak Cluster project promises to
OL,7,F"secure the future" of almost half of
OL,8,Fthe country's cement and lime
OL,9,Findustry, while also being "vital" to
OL,10,Fthe Government's plans to hit net zero
OL,11,Fby 2050.
OL,13,FGovernment projections suggest the
OL,14,Fproject could protect up to 13,000
OL,15,Fjobs while the wider carbon capture
OL,16,Fsector could provide 50,000 jobs over
OL,17,Fthe next twenty years.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773159076
OL,3,CHundreds of Wirral residents protest
OL,4,Cagainst Peak Cluster pipeline
OL,6,FThe Peak Cluster CEO John Egan says
OL,7,Fthe Wirral was seen as the most
OL,8,Ffeasible route to the Irish Sea,
OL,9,Fchosen over areas from North Wales to
OL,10,FCumbria.
OL,12,FResponding to environmental concerns,
OL,13,FPeak Cluster said: "Once construction
OL,14,Fends, we will reinstate the majority
OL,15,Fof the land so it can be used in the
OL,16,Fsame way as it was before and, just as
OL,17,Fwith other pipelines under our feet,
OL,18,Fthe land will look and feel just as it
OL,19,Fdid before."
OL,26,@uD@TOU{D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773159076
OL,3,CHundreds of Wirral residents protest
OL,4,Cagainst Peak Cluster pipeline
OL,6,FThe Labour Government has hit back at
OL,7,Fcalls from within its own party to
OL,8,Fscrap the project while also
OL,9,Fhighlighting the importance of Peak
OL,10,FCluster.
OL,12,FDepartment for Energy Security and Net
OL,13,FZero spokesperson said: "Carbon
OL,14,Fcapture, usage and storage is vital
OL,15,Ffor Britain's clean energy future. The
OL,16,FClimate Change Committee describes it
OL,17,Fas a 'necessity not an option' for
OL,18,Freaching our climate goals.
OL,26,@uD@YOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773159076
OL,3,CHundreds of Wirral residents protest
OL,4,Cagainst Peak Cluster pipeline
OL,6,F"We are delivering first of a kind
OL,7,Fcarbon capture projects in the UK,
OL,8,Fbacked by #9.4 billion over this
OL,9,Fparliament ` supporting thousands of
OL,10,Fjobs across the country and reigniting
OL,11,Four industrial heartlands."
OL,13,F"All carbon capture projects must meet
OL,14,Fstrict environmental and regulatory
OL,15,Frequirements, including ensuring high
OL,16,Flevels of protection for both
OL,17,Fcommunities and the environment."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@[O]uD@AOUyD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773159076
OL,3,CHundreds of Wirral residents protest
OL,4,Cagainst Peak Cluster pipeline
OL,6,FConservationists say it is "too early
OL,7,Fto say" whether they agree with the
OL,8,Fproject, but have expressed concern
OL,9,Fover the impacts on nature.
OL,11,FCharlotte Harris, Chief Executive of
OL,12,Fthe Cheshire Wildlife Trust said: "We
OL,13,Fcan't solve the climate crisis by
OL,14,Fmaking the nature crisis worse.
OL,16,F"Our role is that nature is protected
OL,17,Fand we put nature in recovery. Any
OL,18,Flarge infrastructure scheme like this
OL,19,Fneeds to leave nature in a better
OL,20,Fstate than it is in currently.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773159076
OL,3,CHundreds of Wirral residents protest
OL,4,Cagainst Peak Cluster pipeline
OL,6,F"We all rely on nature, we can't live
OL,7,Fwithout nature. We have to protect
OL,8,Fwhat is here and when we are already
OL,9,Fin an area and a country which is
OL,10,Fnature-depleted, we can't afford to
OL,11,Flose any more.
OL,13,FShe added: "The scheme is at a really
OL,14,Fearly stage. There is a lot of
OL,15,Fconsultation to go yet. At the moment
OL,16,Fwe are assessing the potential impacts
OL,17,Fto understand what they might be."
OL,19,FWhat is the Peak Cluster Project?
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773159076
OL,3,CHundreds of Wirral residents protest
OL,4,Cagainst Peak Cluster pipeline
OL,6,FThe Labour Government announced it
OL,7,Fwould be launching a carbon capture
OL,8,Fstorage project in 2023, which would
OL,9,Frun from the Peak District, through
OL,10,Fthe Wirral, to the Irish Sea.
OL,12,FThe project, known as Peak Cluster,
OL,13,Fwould carry emissions from four cement
OL,14,Fand lime producers in the Peak
OL,15,FDistrict and release it into
OL,16,Funderground gas fields.
OL,18,FIt is hoped the project would prevent
OL,19,Fthe harmful emissions from entering
OL,20,Fthe atmosphere and help the Government
OL,21,Fhit their net zero targets.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773159076
OL,3,CHundreds of Wirral residents protest
OL,4,Cagainst Peak Cluster pipeline
OL,6,FA consultation document explained that
OL,7,Fthe cement and lime industry is unable
OL,8,Fto avoid producing carbon dioxide, so
OL,9,Fcapturing the emissions will help
OL,10,F"secure the future of 40% of Britain's
OL,11,Fcement and lime production industry,
OL,12,Fanchored in Derbyshire and
OL,13,FStaffordshire."
OL,15,FIt went on to say: "The project will
OL,16,Fhelp to protect existing jobs, and
OL,17,Fcreate new roles, while ensuring a
OL,18,Freliable and sustainable supply of
OL,19,Fessential building materials for
OL,20,Fhospitals, homes, railways, and roads."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773159076
OL,3,CHundreds of Wirral residents protest
OL,4,Cagainst Peak Cluster pipeline
OL,6,FThe current route for the 160 mile
OL,7,Fpipeline has it running through
OL,8,FWillaston, Thornton Hough, Barnston,
OL,9,Fand Thurstaston.
OL,11,FThe carbon dioxide would then be
OL,12,Fcompressed at an onshore facility,
OL,13,Fwhich would be built just south of
OL,14,FMeols near Hoylake.
OL,16,FThe pipe would then run into the East
OL,17,FIrish sea where the emissions would be
OL,18,Fdeposited.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39615
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773159076
OL,3,CHundreds of Wirral residents protest
OL,4,Cagainst Peak Cluster pipeline
OL,6,FOverall, the pipeline corridor is to
OL,7,Fbe 300 metres wide and 121 miles long,
OL,8,Fbut this would eventually be narrowed
OL,9,Fdown to 100 metres in width to allow
OL,10,Ffor adjustments, while the actual
OL,11,Fpipes would be around a metre wide,
OL,12,FPeak Cluster diagrams show.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39616
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773159076
OL,3,CHundreds of Wirral residents protest
OL,4,Cagainst Peak Cluster pipeline
OL,6,FOn the long-term effect this could
OL,7,Fhave on the land, Peak Cluster said:
OL,8,F"Once construction ends, we will
OL,9,Freinstate the majority of the land so
OL,10,Fit can be used in the same way as it
OL,11,Fwas before and, just as with other
OL,12,Fpipelines under our feet, the land
OL,13,Fwill look and feel just as it did
OL,14,Fbefore."
OL,16,FA final decision will be made on
OL,17,Fwhether the project goes ahead in 2029.
OL,26,@vD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G16/17
